episodes.title: AUM: The Cult at the End of the World - 2023 Sundance Film Festival
episodes.description:
Presentation of Ben Braun and Chiaki Yanagimoto's AUM: The Cult at the End of the World at the 2023 Sundance Film Festival - Holiday Village theatre. Presentation and post-screening Q&A with the filmmakers.

Please support us by SUBSCRIBING to our Youtube channel!:
https://www.youtube.com/user/ioncinema?sub_confirmation=1

Let us know what you think of AUM: The Cult at the End of the World - leave your comments below!
